author: Connor Creates
description:
An iconic vehicle, reimagined. It was so fun being able to check out the new concept Scout Traveler SUV…and it was love at first sight. Legit the most well-designed and beautiful vehicle I’ve seen! Every little detail is so well thought out and meeting the team I could definitely see how much passion has gone into it. 

Thanks @scoutmotors  for making me a car guy now 
#ScoutMotors
title: My First Look at the Scout Traveller SUV (prototype)
